            "SpeakerIconId": "303"
        },
        {
            "Id": 142442013,
            "EpisodeMasterId": 142442,
            "Order": 1,
            "GroupOrder": 13,
            "SpeakerName": "雪",
            "FontSize": 2,
            "Phrase": "（このウェディングドレス、重たいな……。/n　ちょっと角度を変えるだけでも、ひと苦労だ……）",
            "BackgroundCharacterImageFileName": "142440_0",
            "VoiceFileName": "1424420100",
            "CharacterMotions": [],
            "SpeakerIconId": "303"
        },
        {
            "Id": 142442014,
            "EpisodeMasterId": 142442,
            "Order": 1,
            "GroupOrder": 14,
            "SpeakerName": "スタッフ１",
            "FontSize": 2,
            "Phrase": "そしたら次は、三歩前に出て……そう、そこで止まって！/nカメラに向かってもう一度、笑顔をお願いします！",
            "BackgroundCharacterImageFileName": "142440_0",
            "VoiceFileName": "1424420110",
            "CharacterMotions": [],
            "SpeakerIconId": "1"
        },
        {
            "Id": 142442015,
            "EpisodeMasterId": 142442,
            "Order": 1,
            "GroupOrder": 15,
            "SpeakerName": "雪",
            "FontSize": 2,
            "Phrase": "（こ……こうか？/n　しかし、ドレスってのは本当に歩きにくいな……！）",
            "BackgroundCharacterImageFileName": "142440_0",
            "VoiceFileName": "1424420120",
            "CharacterMotions": [],
            "SpeakerIconId": "303"
        },
        {
            "Id": 142442016,
            "EpisodeMasterId": 142442,
            "Order": 1,
            "GroupOrder": 16,
            "SpeakerName": "スタッフ１",
            "FontSize": 2,
            "Phrase": "いいですねー！　バッチリです！",
            "BackgroundCharacterImageFileName": "142440_0",
            "VoiceFileName": "1424420130",
            "CharacterMotions": [],
            "SpeakerIconId": "1"
        },
        {
            "Id": 142442017,
            "EpisodeMasterId": 142442,
            "Order": 1,
            "GroupOrder": 17,
            "SpeakerName": "プロデューサー",
            "FontSize": 2,
            "Phrase": "ほう……この美しさと透明感……！/nさすがは銀河座の役者というべきか……。",
            "BackgroundCharacterImageFileName": "142440_0",
            "VoiceFileName": "1424420140",
            "CharacterMotions": [],
            "SpeakerIconId": "1"
        },
        {
            "Id": 142442018,
            "EpisodeMasterId": 142442,
            "Order": 1,
            "GroupOrder": 18,
            "SpeakerName": "プロデューサー",
            "FontSize": 2,
            "Phrase": "図らずも、良い収穫だ。/nこれなら読者からも反響がありそうだ……！",
            "BackgroundCharacterImageFileName": "142440_0",
            "VoiceFileName": "1424420150",
            "CharacterMotions": [],
            "SpeakerIconId": "1"
        },
        {
            "Id": 142442019,
            "EpisodeMasterId": 142442,
            "Order": 1,
            "GroupOrder": 19,
            "SpeakerName": "雪",
            "FontSize": 2,
            "Phrase": "（くっ……全部口に出てるぞ……！/n　そんなにべた褒めされたら気恥ずかしいだろ……！）",
            "BackgroundCharacterImageFileName": "142440_0",
            "VoiceFileName": "1424420160",
            "CharacterMotions": [],
            "SpeakerIconId": "303"
        },
        {
            "Id": 142442020,
            "EpisodeMasterId": 142442,
            "Order": 1,
            "GroupOrder": 20,
            "SpeakerName": "雪",
            "FontSize": 2,
            "Phrase": "（いやダメだ、落ち着け……。/n　ワタシは今、『幸せの絶頂にいる花嫁』なんだ……）",
            "BackgroundCharacterImageFileName": "142440_0",
            "VoiceFileName": "1424420170",
            "CharacterMotions": [],
            "SpeakerIconId": "303"
        },
        {
            "Id": 142442021,
            "EpisodeMasterId": 142442,
            "Order": 1,
            "GroupOrder": 21,
            "SpeakerName": "雪",
            "FontSize": 2,
            "Phrase": "（最後まで集中を切らすな……！/n　これはワタシが主役の、ワタシの舞台……！）",
            "BackgroundCharacterImageFileName": "142440_0",
            "VoiceFileName": "1424420180",
